            <lb/><forename>Leonarde</forename> et <forename>peyronne</forename><surname>lendrys</surname> filhes de feu <forename>mathias</forename> et <forename><expan>perine</expan></forename><lb/><surname>lendriz</surname> appellans du seneschal de <placeName>lymosin</placeName> ou son <expan>lieutenant</expan> au
            <lb/>siege de <placeName>lymoges</placeName><choice><orig>dune</orig><reg>d’une</reg></choice> part
            <lb/>Et <persName><forename>gouffier</forename><nameLink>de</nameLink><surname>la plasse</surname><roleName><expan>sieur</expan></roleName> de <placeName>la brousse</placeName></persName> appelle <choice><orig>daultre</orig><reg>d’aultre</reg></choice></ab><ab><lb/>Veu le proces Libelle appellatoire <expan>responce</expan> a <expan>icelluy</expan></ab><ab><lb/>Il sera dict que la court met <choice><orig>lappel</orig><reg>l’appel</reg></choice> et ce dont a este
            <lb/>appelle au neant Et sens <choice><orig>auoir</orig><reg>avoir</reg></choice> esgard aulx causes <expan><choice><orig>dopposition</orig><reg>d’opposition</reg></choice></expan><lb/><expan>desdits</expan> appellans <expan>ladite</expan> court ordonne <expan>que</expan><expan>ledit</expan> de la plasse
            <lb/>et <expan>consors</expan> pourront venir a <choice><orig><expan>diuision</expan></orig><reg><expan>division</expan></reg></choice> et <expan>partaige</expan> de la <expan>proprieté</expan><lb/>du lieu de <placeName>la brousse</placeName> et <expan>pour</expan> ce <expan>faire</expan> sacorderont <choice><orig>darbitres</orig><reg>d’arbitres</reg></choice><lb/>dens ung moys prochenement venent <expan>pardevant</expan><expan>ledit</expan> seneschal ou
            <lb/><expan>sondit</expan><expan>lieutenant</expan> Oste <expan>que</expan><sic><expan>lesdits</expan></sic> appellant et ses <expan>consortz</expan><lb/>demeureront mestayers perpetuelz, <expan>audit</expan> lieu de <placeName>la brousse</placeName><lb/><choice><orig>suyuent</orig><reg>suyvent</reg></choice> le <expan>contraict</expan> de baliete et offres <expan>mentionnes</expan><expan>audit</expan><lb/>proces le tout sens <expan><choice><orig>preiudice</orig><reg>prejudice</reg></choice></expan> des <expan>autres</expan> droitz <expan>pretendus</expan><lb/>par les appellans en vertu de la baliete de la 
            <lb/>mesterie <expan>perpetuelle</expan><expan>Reparations</expan> et <expan>meliorations</expan> par eulx
